{"tid":61410,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"人中之龍系列戰鬥力最強既角色係邊個","createTime":"2016-12-31T08:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-01T10:27:16.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"15b785ee0c739813b1c7873673649b8709b42ba4","tid":61410,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"桐生一馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冴島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真島<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5039f39442216d1f02b1f33ab2b395ead528e0a7","tid":61410,"uid":21388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"有無得揀吾朗美"},{"pid":"7c2db1e54b5288d538bce4d179d591c5bd03cfa0","tid":61410,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:22:18.000Z","msg":"有邊個能夠同熊打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40cf9c3b5842b2d0b83e2aedc0681f72894c9ebc","tid":61410,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T08:29:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊個能夠同熊打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冴島身體質素真係好恐佈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffb58036c2636e37fb2626d6d55404ba2633c603","tid":61410,"uid":21388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T11:18:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊個能夠同熊打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n桐生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2befe5e62504ba7d57d89051098b53186e3cfc3d","tid":61410,"uid":45498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-31T18:47:25.000Z","msg":"冴島&gt;桐生&gt;真島<br />\n冴島逃獄出海後沖上岸，受傷情況下與桐生打成平手，應該更耐打，力量更大，技巧方面桐生有優勢<br />\n真島除咗0之外 受年紀問題影響 實力應該退快得較快<br />\n<br />\n但0時期 真島&gt;桐生"},{"pid":"0d5443a27cfc7d83fd3142ea40ddb07ce6c28ded","tid":61410,"uid":1533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T06:25:50.000Z","msg":"秋山&gt;大吾？"},{"pid":"ba760e147f09e46b85be06795546c3d1902e74b9","tid":61410,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T08:24:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>秋山&amp;gt;大吾？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n秋山勁定品田勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487c115f648e2672bcd61391c8a62cc285037052","tid":61410,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T09:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有邊個能夠同熊打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n桐生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n桐生頭兩集可以秒獅子老虎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b94d43e38eb4473680065f6618d80dfa66566612","tid":61410,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冴島&gt;桐生&gt;真島<br />\n冴島逃獄出海後沖上岸，受傷情況下與桐生打成平手，應該更耐打，力量更大，技巧方面桐生有優勢<br />\n真島除咗0之外 受年紀問題影響 實力應該退快得較快<br />\n<br />\n但0時期 真島&gt;桐生</blockquote><br />\n你睇人中5冴島冇傷嘅情況下有冇打贏桐生，已經唔比較渡瀨同勝矢邊個勁啲，人中4冴島傷口一爆已經打唔到，所以佢兩個係平手，冴島係天生神力超力量型，桐生就綜合格鬥型，1988年真島一定勁過桐生，1995冇打過，我估應該差不多，2005最後個真島支線，真島都同意桐生話2005嘅堂島之龍＞1995堂島之龍"},{"pid":"b955d247a0a340de1f0f3d8c87bc9a88779e6431","tid":61410,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>秋山&amp;gt;大吾？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n秋山勁定品田勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n品田打贏大吾之後，個cg係大吾扶喘氣嘅品田起身，我估大吾未盡全力，人中2桐生第一次打龍司得一條血，第二第三次係三條血，就係因為大吾同龍司之前打左一場，扣左佢大半血，桐生同龍司講自己輕鬆贏係因為大吾係強勁嘅對手，下次先公平同龍司打，雖然秋山，錦，大吾冇正面對決過，但我感覺係大吾＞錦＞秋山"},{"pid":"c7253960cb6cc95561f859b286fdab96f54cc1d9","tid":61410,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-01T10:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有邊個能夠同熊打過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n桐生囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n桐生頭兩集可以秒獅子老虎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n桐生人中2喺有刀傷嘅情況下，打死左兩隻老虎，人中3打死左三隻蠻牛"}]}